																		                else to_char(rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when nvl(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when nvl(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when nvl(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 100) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 100  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 100 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and nvl(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = nvl(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and nvl(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = nvl(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  100))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X
-----------------------------------------------------

Data:    31.01.2020 10:31:07
Pagina:    General
Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else

															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end

                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0

	                case

		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"

									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User",

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 3  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 3 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16

						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"

								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"

                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=253 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=253 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=253 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=253 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"
                        WHERE (A."IdUser"=253 OR A.F10003=253)) X

                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=253) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 253) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 253  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=253 AND 253 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  253))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != 253)) 
                ) X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"
                        WHERE (A."IdUser"=3 OR A.F10003=-99)) X

												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 3  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 3 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  3))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case

						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"
                        WHERE (A."IdUser"=3 OR A.F10003=-99)) X

                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  3))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case

		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",

                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 3  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 3 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"
                        WHERE (A."IdUser"=3 OR A.F10003=-99)) X

                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
