Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"

								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"

                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case

	                                    end, -99)

                                PIVOT  (MAX("ValStr") FOR "Ziua" IN (  [2019-12-01], [2019-12-02], [2019-12-03], [2019-12-04], [2019-12-05], [2019-12-06], [2019-12-07], [2019-12-08], [2019-12-09], [2019-12-10], [2019-12-11], [2019-12-12], [2019-12-13], [2019-12-14], [2019-12-15], [2019-12-16], [2019-12-17], [2019-12-18], [2019-12-19], [2019-12-20], [2019-12-21], [2019-12-22], [2019-12-23], [2019-12-24], [2019-12-25], [2019-12-26], [2019-12-27], [2019-12-28], [2019-12-29], [2019-12-30], [2019-12-31] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                
                                
                                
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare1", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare2", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare3", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare4", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare5", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare6", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare7", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare8", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare9", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare10", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare11", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare12", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare13", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare14", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare15", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare16", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare17", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare18", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare19", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare20", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare21", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare22", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare23", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare24", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare25", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare26", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare27", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare28", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare29", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare30", "CuloareValoare" AS "CuloareValoare31" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, "CuloareValoare", "Ziua" From "Ptj_Intrari_2" WHERE '2019-12-01' <= CAST("Ziua" AS date) AND CAST("Ziua" AS date) <= '2019-12-31') source  
                                PIVOT (MAX("CuloareValoare") FOR "Ziua" IN (  [2019-12-01], [2019-12-02], [2019-12-03], [2019-12-04], [2019-12-05], [2019-12-06], [2019-12-07], [2019-12-08], [2019-12-09], [2019-12-10], [2019-12-11], [2019-12-12], [2019-12-13], [2019-12-14], [2019-12-15], [2019-12-16], [2019-12-17], [2019-12-18], [2019-12-19], [2019-12-20], [2019-12-21], [2019-12-22], [2019-12-23], [2019-12-24], [2019-12-25], [2019-12-26], [2019-12-27], [2019-12-28], [2019-12-29], [2019-12-30], [2019-12-31] )) pvt
                                ) pvtCuloare ON X.F10003=pvtPauza.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 12 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-12-31') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 12 
                                ORDER BY NumeComplet) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003=1019

	                case

                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 12 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin

                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741

							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                ORDER BY NumeComplet) A

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)

	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'

										                     end
							                       end

					                      end
			                      end

		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"

                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",

		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case

																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end

		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1

		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",

		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",

		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=1892 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE

									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'

                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/

		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",

	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")

						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")

										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",

		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")

				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")

Data:    04.02.2020 09:22:31
Pagina:    General
Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 1904),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=1904),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=1904),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=1904) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 1904) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 1904  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=1904 AND 1904 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  1904))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != 1904)) 
                ) X

		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 1236) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 1236  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=1924 AND 1236 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  1236))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != 1924)) 
                ) X
